        public static Browser.BrowserName lookup(String b)
                                  throws InvalidBrowserException
        allows the browser selected to be passed in with a case insensitive name
        Parameters:
        b - - the string name of the browser
        Returns:
        Browser: the enum version of the browser
        Throws:
